Name: The Nimbus Chorale: Soil of Abundance
AttributesDescription: A musical record found in Nimbus Sanctum. This chorale was performed by the people of Rinascita long before the Order's founding.
BgDescription: "We thank Rinascita, for she embraced us with her fertile lands, offering a shelter to those of us drifting in the winds on the sea. From this day forward, we shall have a place to call home, where our roots embed deeply."
